# Images Directory

This directory contains all static images for the documentation.

## Structure

The directory structure mirrors the documentation hierarchy:

```
public/images/
├── databases/
│   ├── kafka/
│   ├── mysql/
│   ├── postgres/
│   └── redis/
├── devops/
│   ├── ci-cd/
│   └── jenkins/
├── infra/
│   ├── kubernetes/
│   └── storage/
│       ├── csi-drivers/
│       └── nfs/
├── networking/
│   ├── dns/
│   └── ingress-lb/
└── incident-response/
```

## Usage in MDX

Reference images using absolute paths:

```mdx
![Description](/images/category/subcategory/image-name.png)
```

Example:
```mdx
![TrueNAS Portal](/images/infra/kubernetes/truenas-portal.png)
```

Or with Next.js Image component for optimization:
```mdx
import Image from 'next/image'

<Image 
  src="/images/infra/kubernetes/truenas-portal.png" 
  alt="TrueNAS Portal"
  width={800}
  height={600}
/>